\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0 As is tradition, Liz leaves her front door unlocked so that the attendees of the poker party can let themselves in. Being that they are all friends and family, Liz has no safety concerns. As they enter, Liz greets all of her guests with a warm welcoming hug.}
